embeds.title: Money and Gold Pack | 3D Props | Unity Asset Store
embeds.description:
__**Money and Gold is a model/material asset pack that contains:**__
- 5 Seamless Materials
- 48 Textures in total
- 11 Prefabs
- Texture Resolution: 4096 by 4096
- Texture Format: TGA
- Texture Type: Seamless

__**Project Benefits**__
- Great for a cop and robbers game!
- 4 Different Gold Bars, with LODs, 2 versions
- Double-sided bills, 2 versions
- Single-sided bills, 2 versions
- New,Used, and old Money Stacks
- Old and new money designs
- 4 Money Piles
- Money Box
- Money Wraps, 3 versions
